<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: The remnants of the monolith which linked our world to the void lie broken. The twisted patterns that once writhed across its surface are now motionless. You can study the broken stones to gain further knowledge of the void phenomena. -->
  <Disrupted.monolithDescription>我々の世界とヴォイドを繋いでいたモノリスの残骸が横たわっています.かつてその表面をうごめいていた捻れた模様は今はもう動いていません.壊れた石を調べることで,ヴォイド現象の知識をさらに得られます.</Disrupted.monolithDescription>
  <!-- EN: collapsed monolith -->
  <Disrupted.monolithLabel>崩壊したモノリス</Disrupted.monolithLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: Level 4: Awakened -->
  <Embraced.levelInspectText>レベル4：覚醒</Embraced.levelInspectText>
  <!-- EN: void monolith -->
  <Embraced.monolithLabel>ヴォイドモノリス</Embraced.monolithLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: The void has awoken. The gate is open. The darkness of the void rushes into our reality, manifested from a vast mind of endless rage. -->
  <Gleaming.extraQuestDescription>ヴォイドが目覚め,ゲートが開かれました.ヴォイドの闇が我々の現実へと押し寄せ,果てしなき怒りの精神より顕現します.</Gleaming.extraQuestDescription>
  <!-- EN: Level 4: Awakened -->
  <Gleaming.levelInspectText>レベル4：覚醒</Gleaming.levelInspectText>
  <!-- EN: void monolith -->
  <Gleaming.monolithLabel>ヴォイドモノリス</Gleaming.monolithLabel>
  
