  <Inactive.activateGizmoDescription>入植者を送ってモノリスを調べます.</Inactive.activateGizmoDescription>
  <!-- EN: investigate -->
  <Inactive.activateGizmoText>調査する</Inactive.activateGizmoText>
  <!-- EN: Send a colonist to investigate the monolith. -->
  <Inactive.activateQuestText>入植者を送ってモノリスを調べます.</Inactive.activateQuestText>
  <!-- EN: Twisting lines carved into the surface form a disturbing pattern. -->
  <Inactive.levelInspectText>表面に刻まれた捻れた線が不穏な模様を描いています.</Inactive.levelInspectText>
  <!-- EN: Can be investigated now. -->
  <Inactive.monolithCanBeActivatedText>今すぐ調査可能.</Inactive.monolithCanBeActivatedText>
